text: He has the money to give whatever but he spoils me with his time. He makes every effort to show me just how important I am. Sick or well, struggling or thriving, he sees me! Even when I doubt my ability to love him properly, he has enough faith for us both.

author: Tania L. Johnson
text:
I understand now. 
Forget the ones who go around saying I love you. Love the ones who love you from your broken place and show you what it is. The one that’s quiet big extremely loud in the amazing effort. I’m grateful for the subtle hints that he listens with his deeds!
